submissionPage.description: Scroll up to change any of your answers. Changing answers may add new questions.

additionalConsentQuestions.text: Can Discover contact you to take part in research studies and surveys to improve healthcare for you and others?

sections.title: Your data
sections.details: We recognise the importance of processing and protecting your personal and health information responsibly and securely. For further information on how Huma process your personal information, please refer to the Privacy Policy.

options.text: I understand that Huma will process my personal data, including health information, as described in the Privacy Policy.

items.description: How often have you been bothered by not being able to stop or control worrying?

answers.question: In the past 4 weeks, have you had a problem with involuntary urinating when laughing or coughing?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had a problem with obtaining or maintaining erections?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had a problem with vaginal dryness during intercourse?
In the past 4 weeks, has pain kept you awake or woken you at night?
In the past 4 weeks, has the touch of bed sheets, clothes, or wearing shoes bothered you?
In the past 4 weeks, have you burned or injured yourself and been unable to feel it?
In the past 4 weeks, have any symptoms kept you from doing your usual activities during the day?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had difficulty doing fine movements with your fingers, like buttoning your clothes, turning pages in a book, picking up coins from a table?
In the past 4 weeks, have you felt unsteady on your feet when you walk?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had any problem getting out of a chair without pushing with your hands?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had a problem walking down stairs?
In the past 4 weeks, have you been unable to feel your feet when walking?
In the past 4 weeks, have you been unable to tell hot from cold water with your hands?
In the past 4 weeks, have you been unable to tell hot from cold water with your feet?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had a problem with vomiting, particularly after meals (but not due to flu or other illness)?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had a problem with diarrhea and/or loss of bowel control?
In the past 4 weeks, have you had a problem with fainting or dizziness when you stand?
In general, would you say your health now is:
Compared with 3 months ago, how would you rate your health in general now?
In the past 4 weeks, to what extent has your physical health interfered with your normal social activities with family, friends, neighbors, or groups?
In the past 4 weeks, how much did pain interfere with your normal work (including work both outside the home and housework)?
In the past 4 weeks, how much did weakness or shakiness interfere with your normal work (including work both outside the home and housework)?
